<https://w3id.org/EVI#inputSize> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The expected input size or shape the model is designed to receive and process at one time. For example, image classificatoin models such as ResNet, VGG commonly use 224x224 pixels with 3 channels while Language Models such as BERT, GPT use tokens or context length from thousand to millions." .
